Create a GitHub OAuth App at github.com/settings/developers

Callback (local): http://localhost:3000/api/auth/callback/github
Callback (production): https://<your-vercel-domain>/api/auth/callback/github
Set environment variables in .env.local and Vercel (see .env.example):

AUTH_SECRET — generate with openssl rand -base64 32
AUTH_GITHUB_ID / AUTH_GITHUB_SECRET — from the OAuth app
ALLOWED_GITHUB_USERNAME — your exact GitHub handle
Redeploy on Vercel after adding the env vars.